data.title: Family Photograph Album
data.meta_description:
Blue-covered album of carte-de-visite size photographs, photographs of portraits, silhouettes and sketches of members of the Galton, Butler, Wheler, Bunbury, and Moilliet families, plus family friends. Most photographs are captioned with the names of the subjects. Some also include biographical information and/or information about the photographer on the reverse.

2. Sarah Maria Butler, nee Gray
